<div id="v520.9.1"><span class="G3004 s">I say</span><span class="G225 s"> the truth</span><span class="G1722 s"> in</span><span class="G5547 s"> Christ</span><span class="G5574 s">, I lie</span><span class="G3756 s"> not</span><span class="G3450 s">, my</span><span class="G4893 s"> conscience</span><span class="G4828 s"> also bearing</span><span class="G3427 s"> me</span><span class="G4828 s"> witness</span><span class="G1722 s"> in</span><span class="G40 s"> the Holy</span><span class="G4151 s"> Ghost</span>,</div>
