<div id="v520.9.3"><span class="G1063 s">For</span><span class="G1473 s"> I</span><span class="G2172 s"> could wish</span><span class="G846 s"> that myself</span><span class="G1511 s"> were</span><span class="G331 s"> accursed</span><span class="G575 s"> from</span><span class="G5547 s"> Christ</span><span class="G5228 s"> for</span><span class="G3450 s"> my</span><span class="G80 s"> brethren</span><span class="G3450 s">, my</span><span class="G4773 s"> kinsmen</span><span class="G2596 s"> according</span><span class="G4561 s"> to the flesh</span>: <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators: (accursed: or, separated)</span></div>
